window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Bran returns to Vein City to find Gloria jealous that he came back with Nyx and Circe. While trying to solve that, Vincent becomes even pushier about entering the Vault.<br> When going to open it, Bran discovers that this life has changed yet again. For whatever reason, they had gotten perilously close to cracking the Vault on their own and drawing all the future heroes of the First Demon War in a demonic trap.<br> It's up to Bran to make sure they all make it out alive while reaping as much reward as he can from the Vault.</p>"; 
